research/history/round_summaries/round_0218.json:73:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u6211\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf `expert_topk` \u505a\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u518d\u9009 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` \u6216 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a r217 \u5df2\u7ed9\u51fa factorized shared+routed \u6781\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u800c\u540e\u8005\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u4e5f\u5df2\u6709\u660e\u663e\u4e0d\u7a33\u5386\u53f2\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u4e4b\u4e0b\uff0c`shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u66f4\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7684\u201c\u4e0d\u5bf9\u79f0 coarse \u4e3b\u5e72 + residual cleanup\u201d\u5047\u8bbe\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u8fd8\u6ca1\u6709\u5728\u5f53\u524d matched recipe \u4e0a\u505a\u8fc7\u4e00\u6b21\u5e72\u51c0 probe\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u6309 exact cost \u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u5b83\u8981\u8d62\u8fc7 r212 \u9700\u8981 exceed \u76f4\u63a5\u6253\u5230\u7ea6 0.1407\uff0c\u95e8\u69db\u975e\u5e38\u9ad8\uff1b\u6240\u4ee5\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u4fdd\u5b88\u8d62\u9762\u6700\u5927\u7684\u9009\u62e9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u9ad8\u98ce\u9669\u3001\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u88c1\u51b3\u3002\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u843d\u540e\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u5408\u7406\u5224\u65ad\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a shared-lowrank-coarse \u8fd9\u6761\u7ebf\u77ed\u671f\u5185\u4e0d\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u5360\u636e\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:37:      "最近低成本 probes 已给出负信号：r176 的 routed-only `expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下仍明显偏弱，r177 的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下更差；当前这一步是更符合新策略提示的“cheap shared/coarse + residual experts”结构测试。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0127.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0127.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，B^sh 与各 routed expert 子库 B_e 都是真正静态向量库。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection -> router 选少量 routed experts -> shared 子库 local top-k + routed 子库 local top-k -> 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表流水线，兼容性判断为直接兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是不兼容，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：当前最缺的新结构信息不是继续细扫现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是提示中明确要求的异构 MoE 新槽位“shared experts + routed experts”叠加 expert 内部 low-rank scorer。相对 r108 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到新实现的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变，直接回答“shared+routed + shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”是否能在更低 encoder 成本下保住 shared+routed 的质量优势。按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，这个结构的 selection cost 将明显低于 r108 的 full-dim shared+routed scorer，而 deployment cost 保持同量级，因此有机会把 total_cost 压到约 0.25x 左右，同时仍明显优于当前 <0.5x 区域的旧 anchor。",
