research/history/logs/agent_action_0219.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式写为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`，其中 `h(x)` 是 shared low-rank bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是静态 shared/coarse 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared low-rank 主干查表 + 轻量 router 选少量 expert 子库 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`expert_topk`、`shared_routed_expert_topk` 等仍是兼容 family；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属 `不兼容`，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：r217 已强烈否定“factorized shared+routed scorer”，r218 又否定了“shared low-rank coarse + two-stage residual cleanup”，因此当前 remaining matched probe 里唯一仍落在 `0.18x~0.22x` 主战场、且还能直接回答高优先级未决问题的结构槽位，是更简单的 `shared low-rank trunk + routed experts`。相对 r212 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 以及其余主 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank trunk 本身是否值得保留，还是一旦去掉 explicit residual cleanup 就会再次让 exceed 失控”。本地复核显示该点 selection_accesses=737280、deployment_acced capacity。"]}
