research/history/logs/agent_action_0144.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i 是 shared low-rank coarse stage 的重构，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r143 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”是否能在约 0.30x total_cost 下优于当前刚形成的新 lowrank+expert 低成本锚点。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.30x 下明显优于 r143，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，继续定位 coarse/residual 的低成本分工边界。","如果结果只与 r143 接近，则说明把 trunk 从全局 lowrank 改成 shared low-rank coarse stage 的结构收益有限，后续可优先转向带全局 residual 的三段式结构，而不是继续打磨这条两段式线。","如果新 family 明显劣于 r143，则可以更明确地把当前 low-cost 主线保留在 `lowrank_expert_topk`，同时下调 shared-lowrank two-stage 方向优先级。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，真实改动仅在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","按 `sae-architecture-integration` 做了 exact architecture smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 已可 instantiate/forward/backward。","成本自检：selection_accesses=794624、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1253376，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.30，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":143,"self_review":"这轮满足运行时单变量原则：计划运行时相对 r143 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 刚形成新低成本 anchor 之后，继续在其内部做局部扫参会过早收缩搜索空间；新增一个最小可运行的两段式原型 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，更符合当前阶段对“shared experts + routed experts / two-stage residual expert”结构槽位的补证据需求。代码改动严格限制在 `sparsify/`，并已完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class 和 exact architecture smoke。主要风险是用 shared low-rank coarse stage 替代 full lowrank trunk 可能损失一部分全局主干表达，但这正是本轮要验证的结构问题。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`：用 shared low-rank coarse stage 先做第一段重构，再让 expert residual stage 处理剩余结构。建议本轮以 r143 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，直接测试这条新的两段式 hetero MoE 结构能否在约 0.30x total_cost 下形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0227.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `group_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_g(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，其中 `S_g(x)` 由分组竞争后的 top-k 支持形成机制给出，`{b_i}` 是单个静态向量库中的原子。在线导出链路仍是“分组打分/选择 + 静态库查表 + 有限加权求和 + 选择性在线补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为 `直接兼容`。`expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`shared_routed_expert_topk` 等仍属兼容 family；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属 `不兼容`，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：Round 220 的 `factorized_topk` 与 Round 226 的 `jumprelu` 已把“更轻 scorer”与“阈值支持形成”两条单库线都裁成强负信号，但这还没有回答另一个仍未在当前 `K=32` anchor recipe 上干净裁决的问题：如果当前 exceed 的一部分来自支持过度集中在少数相关原子上，那么在不增加 active path 长度、也不引入 expert/router 的前提下，分组竞争能否显著改善 tail error。因而相对 r212 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `group_topk`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余主 recipe 不变，直接裁决“单库 + grouped support competition”这条剩余 direct-compatible selector 槽位是否值得继续。本地精确成本复核显示该点 selection_accesses=1048576、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=1212416，对当前 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy 的 exact total_cost_ratio=0.2890625；若要刷新 r212 的 objective=0.35553750753402713，需要 exceed_alpha_0.50 压到约 `≤0.06647500753402712`。这个门槛很激进，但它仍比那些 `0.38x+`、在 objective 上已先验无赢面的未测 family 更有现实意义；而且相较 `topk`，`group_topk` 提供了当前剩余 selector 家族里更高的信息增量，因为它真正改变了支持形成的竞争结构，而不只是回到 plain 单库稀疏和。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `group_topk@K32` 仍然给出 `exceed_alpha_0.50 > 0.10` 或 objective 明显落后于 r212，则当前 target 上的 direct-compatible single-library selector 变体可整体降级，不再继续消耗 matched architecture probe 在 `topk/group_topk/jumprelu` 线上。","如果该 probe 的 objective 接近但仍明显落后于 r212，说明 grouped competition 只带来次级收益，不足以支撑当前目标；后续只应把这条线保留为历史参考，而不应进入主线。","如果该 probe 意外明显优于 r226 `jumprelu` 并接近可赢门槛，则下一轮才值得继续留在 single-library closure 线上，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=topk` 做同成本对照，区分收益来自 grouped competition 还是单库路径本身。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 226 已确认 `jumprelu@K32` 为强负信号：`objective=0.599505`、`cost=0.289062x`、`exceed=0.310443`，说明单库 selector 里“只改阈值支持形成”不足以把 exceed 拉回可赢区间。","当前 `0.13x~0.21x` 的 matched architecture probes 也已连续给出负信号：`factorized_expert_topk`、`factorized_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`、`shared_routed_expert_topk` 都未把 objective 拉回 r212 附近。","本轮选择 `group_topk` 的原因是：在当前 remaining compatible families 里，它与 `topk/jumprelu` 一样保留 exact total_cost_ratio=0.2890625 的非零理论赢面，但比 plain `topk` 具有更高结构信息增量，因为它真正改变了支持竞争结构。","本地 allowlist 校验通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: ARCHITECTURE, value: group_topk}], fallback_architecture='expert_topk')` 返回空列表。","本地成本复核：`group_topk K=32 EF=1` 在当前 matched recipe 下 selection_accesses=1048576、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=1212416、exact total_cost_ratio=0.2890625。"],"reference_round":212,"self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r212 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，没有新增参数，也没有代码改动。没有再选 `whitened_topk`、`codebook_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 等未测 family，是因为本地 exact cost 复核显示它们在当前 matched recipe 下都落在 `0.38x+` 或更高，已经在 objective 上先验无法刷新 incumbent；继续测试它们更像质量锚点，不符合本轮“matched architecture probe”优先回答 objective 槽位价值的要求。也没有直接回到 `topk`，因为在 `jumprelu` 已明确失败后，plain topk 的新增信息量低于 `group_topk`；如果连 grouped competition 都不能显著改善 exceed，那么 plain 单库线更没有继续价值。主要风险同样明确：它要赢过 r212 需要把 exceed 直接打到约 `0.0665`，现实门槛极高，所以这更像 remaining selector slot 的 closure probe，而不是高置信翻盘点。","summary":"建议以 r212 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=group_topk`。这轮继续做 matched architecture probe，但不再赌更重结构，而是用 single-library selector 剩余槽位里信息增量最高的一点，直接裁决“支持竞争结构本身是否还能带来足以影响 objective 的收益”。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/round0042_standard_1774725657.config.json:15:  "family_stage": "prototype",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0070.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Final reconstruction stays x_hat = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r + sum_{i in S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} alpha_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}, with t(x) = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r. This exports to the LUTurbo/Lottable path as a static trunk table lookup plus a single routed static expert sublibrary lookup plus a finite weighted sum, so `lowrank_expert_topk` is extended-compatible. Compatibility screen before proposing this round: `expert_topk` is directly compatible; `lowrank_expert_topk`, `lowrank_expert_residual`, and `two_stage_residual_expert` are extended-compatible; batch-coupled families such as `batch_topk` and `adaptive_budget_topk` are incompatible and must stay off the active frontier. Relative to r60, changing only `TRUNK_RANK` from 64 to 32 tests the missing mid-trunk point in the low-cost band: if the routed-only improvement from r59 to r60 was not all-or-nothing, this should recover much of r60's FVU while moving left from the current lowrank+expert anchor and potentially create a new compatible Pareto segment between `expert_topk` and `lowrank_expert_residual`.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `TRUNK_RANK=32` keeps most of r60 quality at materially lower total_cost, next do a matched `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual` switch from this point to measure whether residual cleanup is still worth paying for at the same trunk width.","If `TRUNK_RANK=32` falls back close to the routed-only `expert_topk` band, treat that as evidence that `lowrank_expert_topk` has a sharp trunk-width floor and shift low-cost budget back to `lowrank_expert_residual` or pure `expert_topk` rather than more MoE-capacity expansion.","If throughput or convergence looks anomalous rather than simply worse, use a follow-up midpoint such as `TRUNK_RANK=48` before drawing a structural conclusion."],"notes_to_memory":["Round 70 targets the under-mapped low-to-mid-cost region with a structural width probe, not another plain-K sweep.","`lowrank_expert_topk` now has informative anchors at `TRUNK_RANK=16` and `64` under `K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=32`; `TRUNK_RANK=32` is the clean missing midpoint for the same compatible family.","Keep incompatible batch-coupled families excluded from frontier accounting; active frontier decisions should continue to use only direct-compatible and extended-compatible families."],"reference_round":60,"self_review":"This satisfies the single-variable param-only rule and stays within an already implemented compatible family. It directly answers a higher-value structural question than another `expert_topk` K move, and it avoids spending Round 70 on further local polishing of the current `lowrank_expert_residual` mainline after r66 already showed diminishing returns from more trunk compression there.","summary":"Use Round 70 for a low-cost structural probe in `lowrank_expert_topk`: start from r60 and only reduce `TRUNK_RANK` to 32. The goal is to map whether shared low-rank trunk width can produce a new compatible Pareto point in the 0.3x-0.5x band, instead of continuing plain-selector K sweeps or more local cleanup on `lowrank_expert_residual`.","touched_files":[]}
